Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Eastern Pangasinan/Asingan School of Arts and Trades in the Municipality of Asingan, Province of Pangasinan, to Luciano Millan Memorial School of Arts and Trades
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 772
An Act Changing the Name of the Eastern Pangasinan/Asingan School of Arts and Trades in the Municipality of Asingan, Province of Pangasinan, to Luciano Millan Memorial School of Arts and Trades
Section 1. The name of the Eastern Pangasinan/Asingan School of Arts and Trades in the Municipality of Asingan, Province of Pangasinan, is hereby changed to Luciano Millan Memorial School of Arts and Trades.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
